    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get the education part, but doesn't that also mean people just stay on benefits longer because they don't have to work? i've read a lot about how these programs actually discourage people from re-entering the workforce if the benefits are too high. isn't there a real risk of creating a dependency that lowers overall productivity?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
